    {
      "id": "view-hosts",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Host + Datatype",
      "position": {
        "x": 80,
        "y": 80
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Intent + Payload\n\n`data.view.intent` declares purpose.\n`data.view.payload` declares format/runtime.\n\nExamples:\n- `intent: node`, `payload: twilite.web`\n- `intent: panel`, `payload: twilite.web`\n- `intent: preview`, `payload: twilite.svg`\n\nIntent is semantic. Payload is technical.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
